reviewText: There's nothing wrong with this movie. Anyone who prefers watching films in Spanish would understand it and enjoy it.  No different than any other foreign language film. It needs to be made clear, however that the film is in Spanish for English speakers that are not educated other languages.

I purchased this dvd and was so disappointed that I just throw it to the dustbin.
It has vhs quality, no audio original version, only latinspanish dubbing. Brutally scruciating!
Do not buy it!
